title: Latvia Unemployed Persons
description: The number of unemployed persons in Latvia increased to 50278 in October of 2022 from 50194 in September of 2022. Unemployed Persons in Latvia averaged 88774.94  from 1993 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 194253  in March of 2010 and a record low of 36690  in January of 1993. In Latvia, unemployed persons are individuals who are without a job and actively seeking to work. This page provides - Latvia Unemployed Persons - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: State Employment Agency, Latvia
